data.description: If you are looking for privacy and a peaceful setting, this is it! 3 bedroom, 2 full bath home sitting on 4 acres. Nice open floor plan and the Primary Bedroom is on one side and the other two bedrooms are on the other side. This acreage includes an extra 2 acre wooded lot with a stream. The extra lot has a separate tax identification number and can even be sold or kept for privacy or maybe a family member to build. The home has new wood flooring, newer heat pump and the roof is about 10 years old. No carpet! All appliances stay along with the clothes washer/dryer, love seat and kitchen table w/ chairs. The living room has a built-in propane heater in case the power goes out!  There is a long, paved driveway leading to the home. Outside you will find a carport, storage shed, gazebo and fire pit to relax by. You can sit back in the gazebo and watch the abundant wildlife! There is an old barn at the front of the property that might can be restored. Bring your fishing gear as Philpott Lake is approximately THREE miles down the road.  No restrictions here! You can easily put up some fencing and make a micro-farm! Live here and enjoy your privacy and nature!
